query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS contract_modification_logs (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  contractId INT NOT NULL,
  modificationRequestId INT,
  fieldName VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  oldValue TEXT,
  newValue TEXT,
  modifiedBy INT NOT NULL,
  modifiedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (contractId) REFERENCES contracts_enhanced(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (modificationRequestId) REFERENCES contract_modification_requests(id),
  FOREIGN KEY (modifiedBy) REFERENCES users(id)
);
